milestones.description: Esmeijer and Schiferli's 22-run partnership is NED's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 9 between Marcel Schewe and Bas Zuiderent
Tim de Leede has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (6) for NED, going past Aponso
